{"tid":2356170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發］ 灣仔起步突然宣布解散","createTime":"2021-01-06T15:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T03:08:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":370,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"6287bb7ebdba2403b391669d28938479f022ca07","tid":2356170,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"香港警察國安處今晨拘捕 53 名民主派初選組織及參與者，指控他們違反國安法，當中包括灣仔區議會主席楊雪盈。由她牽頭成立的地區組織「灣仔起步」今晚（6 日）在 Facebook 宣布，即日起解散組織並停止運作。<br />\n<br />\n「灣仔起步」指，各個成員會繼續擇善固執，以其他方式延續並守護社區，呼籲市民不要心灰氣餒，「砥礪前行，望香港人能繼續互相支持，守望彼此&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3789442527808006/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3789442527808006%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5sg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=d19faf24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3789442527808006/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"593aa380ea2887129c9c8679eb7b2278d8616aa4","tid":2356170,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58339c8e29bf27c4fb25a7b35999d5bf9eb20c44","tid":2356170,"uid":155818,"like":93,"dislike":23,"score":70,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"邊個仲話香港有救?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032700e780cf9ec66e83ff7095ea8b04c3f1f06d","tid":2356170,"uid":1654,"like":94,"dislike":37,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:29:46.000Z","msg":"以為解散左就唔追究咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6d174366412703a1c62a4fc729256006101876","tid":2356170,"uid":3241,"like":170,"dislike":11,"score":159,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:31:03.000Z","msg":"灣仔起步係地區野合作炸喎<br />\n屌你老母而家